<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Post | <%= id %></title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Courgette&family=Rajdhani:wght@500&family=Source+Sans+Pro:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon.png" type="image/x-icon">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-iecdLmaskl7CVkqkXNQ/ZH/XLlvWZOJyj7Yy7tcenmpD1ypASozpmT/E0iPtmFIB46ZmdtAc9eNBvH0H/ZpiBw==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.base.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.home.css">
    </head>

    <body>

        <header class="profile" id="topo">
            <img class="pfp" src="/img/logo-ifspace.png" alt="Foto de Perfil">
            <p class="user-name"><%= posts.autor %></p>
        </header>

        <div class="layout">
            <nav class="nav">
                <ul class="nav-items">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a href="#topo" class="btn"><i class="fa-regular fa-circle-up fa-lg"></i> Voltar ao topo</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/home/profile" class="btn"><i class="fa-regular fa-address-card fa-lg"></i> Perfil</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/home" class="btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-house-user fa-lg"></i> Página Inicial</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/post" class="btn"><i class="fa-regular fa-paper-plane fa-lg"></i> Postar</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a href="/home/logout" class="btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket fa-lg"></i> LogOut</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav> 

            <div class="container">

                <main class="post-container">
                    <header class="post-header">
                        <h1 class="title"><%= posts.titulo %></h1>
                    </header>
                    <section class="post-section">
                        <p><%= posts.texto %></p>
                    </section>
                    <div class="reactions">
                        <button class="btn"><%= posts.likes %></button>

                        <button class="btn">Seguir</button>
                    </div>
                </main>

                <aside>
                    <header>
                        <h2 class="title">Comentários</h2>
                    </header>
                    <article class="comment">
                        <div class="post-profile">
                            <img src="/img/logo-ifspace.png" alt="logo">
                        <p>Fulaninho</p>
                        </div>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequuntur,
                            illum? Animi illo nobis est iusto mollitia,
                            consequuntur eius, quas, unde quisquam expedita sapiente dignissimos architecto.</p>
                    </article>
                
                    <article class="comment">
                        <div class="post-profile">
                            <img src="/img/logo-ifspace.png" alt="logo">
                        <p>Ciclaninho</p>
                        </div>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequuntur,
                            consequuntur eius, quas, unde quisquam expedita sapiente dignissimos architecto.</p>
                    </article>              
                
                    <article class="comment">
                        <div class="post-profile">
                            <img src="/img/logo-ifspace.png" alt="logo">
                        <p>Juninho</p>
                        </div>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum consequuntur eius, quas, unde quisquam expedita sapiente dignissimos architecto.</p>
                    </article>
                </aside>

            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>